HEADWORD: Alethoscope
<hw>A*leth"o*scope</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr. <?/ true
+ <?/ to view.]</ety> <def>An instrument for viewing pictures by means
